  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three ways to play:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to beat your highscore in <i>Classic</i> mode, race the clock in a round of <i>Time Attack,</i> or go online for a 1v1 game against a friend or random opponent!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find your Push-To-Talk Key</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every round your Push-to-talk key is assigned to one of the green keys at random. Complete each scene by finding the correct key and speaking into your microphone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/b4d22f053aaa94d27fac1b637ee1e14e.avif?t=1743683187\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras_big/b4d22f053aaa94d27fac1b637ee1e14e.avif?t=1743683187 width=800 height=292 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How Hard can it be?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seriously, its just one key. Give it a push and say something. No, not that one. Not that one either. Come on, just say something already.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/c6dabebde01cae22660cf3832b958e74.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/c6dabebde01cae22660cf3832b958e74.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=141 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speak up!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't just be pushing keys like that. You won't know if you've pressed the right key unless you're speaking into your microphone! Sing, babble, yell- Whatever it takes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/0a53db01310b5ccebc839b053c1fd077.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/0a53db01310b5ccebc839b053c1fd077.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=141 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HEARD.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Way to go! But it took you<i> how long?</i> And<i> how many tries?</i> You can do better than that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/9c8562767a1b8cebcc76cf08b1db69da.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/9c8562767a1b8cebcc76cf08b1db69da.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=201 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oh and there are <strong>HATS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock hats to customize your multiplayer character with by completing scenes and unlocking achievements in each game mode!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three ways to play:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to beat your highscore in <i>Classic</i> mode, race the clock in a round of <i>Time Attack,</i> or go online for a 1v1 game against a friend or random opponent!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find your Push-To-Talk Key</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every round your Push-to-talk key is assigned to one of the green keys at random. Complete each scene by finding the correct key and speaking into your microphone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/b4d22f053aaa94d27fac1b637ee1e14e.avif?t=1743683187\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras_big/b4d22f053aaa94d27fac1b637ee1e14e.avif?t=1743683187 width=800 height=292 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How Hard can it be?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seriously, its just one key. Give it a push and say something. No, not that one. Not that one either. Come on, just say something already.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/c6dabebde01cae22660cf3832b958e74.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/c6dabebde01cae22660cf3832b958e74.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=141 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speak up!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't just be pushing keys like that. You won't know if you've pressed the right key unless you're speaking into your microphone! Sing, babble, yell- Whatever it takes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/0a53db01310b5ccebc839b053c1fd077.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/0a53db01310b5ccebc839b053c1fd077.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=141 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HEARD.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Way to go! But it took you<i> how long?</i> And<i> how many tries?</i> You can do better than that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/9c8562767a1b8cebcc76cf08b1db69da.apng?t=1743683187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442890/extras/9c8562767a1b8cebcc76cf08b1db69da.poster.avif?t=1743683187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=201 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oh and there are <strong>HATS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock hats to customize your multiplayer character with by completing scenes and unlocking achievements in each game mode!</p>",
